k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a8dEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=80357028\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>  。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：下午4時至凌晨1時；星期六、日及公眾假期：晚上８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"95cadab0d00a3e0dd29f8bbdb4f3dec7cbc2eba4","tid":2248440,"uid":216523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d96d84a34eb0c359bb8bf99fe4c2679041a14d1","tid":2248440,"uid":217461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1adaf8e594f5d34427c6794df233acd90ecb02fb","tid":2248440,"uid":216523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T17:21:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T18:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:00:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}